  _playerName: Isn't that what you want?
  _NPCName: LYBL
  _dialogueType: 0
  _startDialogue: 0
  linear:
    _pharases: []
    _responses: []
    _haveResponses: 0
  branching:
  - _Question:
    - ... yeah, it is.
    - No, it isn't.
    _NpcResponses:
    - See? I knew you'd come around.
    - Oh don't give me that.
    nextStepIndices: 0b00000001000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - I've solved all of your problems.
    nextStepIndices: 02000000
  - _Question:
    - Not only did you not solve all of them, you made more!
    _NpcResponses:
    - Clearly we have different definitions of "problem".
    nextStepIndices: 03000000
  - _Question:
    - Finally, something you're right about.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Okay, I think this conversation has gone on long enough.
    nextStepIndices: 04000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You're clearly emotional, and not thinking straight.
    nextStepIndices: 05000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - So I think you should head off to bed, and get a good night's sleep.
    nextStepIndices: 06000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - See you in the morning.
    nextStepIndices: 07000000
  - _Question:
    - No, you won't.
    _NpcResponses:
    - What? Why not?
    nextStepIndices: 08000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to take back control)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Wait what are you-
    nextStepIndices: 09000000
  - _Question:
    - Goodbye, Lybl.
    _NpcResponses:
    - NO WAIT-
    nextStepIndices: 0a000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to choose your own life)
    _NpcResponses:
    - 
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Now then, you should get off to bed.
    nextStepIndices: 0c000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - You're probably quite tired, given that outburst.
    nextStepIndices: 0d000000
  - _Question:
    - Good night Lybl.
    _NpcResponses:
    - See you in the morning!
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
